node.text:
Jake Paul offered UFC fighter Conor McGregor $50 million to fight…

A YouTuber…

$50 million.

If you still think it's a waste of time to be on TikTok, Instagram, or any social media building your brand and getting attention, you're mistaken…

And it could be costing you $50 million.

What opportunities are you overlooking?

node.text:
Chances are, your kids don’t need the amount of time you think they do.
.
They just need you to be fully present when you do spend time together.
.
The money that you make to work a few extra hours could create the foundations that set the rest of their lives up for success.
.
Give them time, but don’t use your kids as an excuse.
.
Show them an example of what can be achieved with commitment and #work.
.
#successtips
